# Smoked Salmon Avocado Rolls

{ rating="3" image="smoked_salmon_rolls.jpg" }
:::
:::

## Ingredients

- [ ] smoked salmon
- [ ] cream cheese (optional, but recommended)
- [ ] avocado
- [ ] carrot
- [ ] cucumber
- [ ] wasabi

## Recipe

1. Sliced all ingredients into long strips then roll

## Notes

1. Adding cream cheese creates a classic Philadelphia roll and helps balance the intense smokiness of the salmon
1. Can mix rice vinegar or lemon juice to help prevent the avocado from browning
